   <title>
      <keyword>chdeschd</keyword>
   </title>
   <shortdesc>The &lt;<keyword>chdeschd</keyword>&gt; option provides a specific label for the
list of descriptions of options that a user must choose to accomplish a step
of a task. The default label overridden by &lt;<keyword>chdeschd</keyword>&gt; is <b>Description</b>.</shortdesc>
